\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs30\b 01. General Information and Scope\b0\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs26\b Project Name\b0\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs22 PRONOS - The first on-chain prediction market focused on Latin America.\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs26\b Vision\b0\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs22 Build the most accessible prediction platform for the Latin American market, where anyone can bet on sports, politics, and culture without needing crypto knowledge, complex wallets, or currency conversion expertise.\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs26\b Launch Goal\b0\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs22 Mainnet live before the 2026 FIFA World Cup (June 14, 2026).\line Allocated budget: $30,000 USD.\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs26\b Current Product URL\b0\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs22 https://pronos.io/mvp/ - password protected staging environment.\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs26\b Blockchain Network: Arbitrum (Ethereum Layer 2)\b0\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs22 The selected deployment network is Arbitrum, Ethereum's optimistic rollup Layer 2.\par
