\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs30\b 02. Smart Contract Architecture\b0\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs26\b BUILT - Contract System\b0\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs22 Custom contracts were built from scratch using Solidity 0.8.24, Foundry, and OpenZeppelin v5.6.1. The architecture is original and optimized for binary markets with dynamic fees.\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs24\b PronosToken.sol - Conditional Tokens (ERC-1155)\b0\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs22 Each market creates two tokens: YES (`marketId * 2`) and NO (`marketId * 2 + 1`).\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 -\tab ERC-1155 standard for gas-efficient multi-market support\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 -\tab Only authorized pools (minters) can mint or burn tokens\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 -\tab `mintPair()`: deposit collateral and receive YES + NO in a 1:1 ratio\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 -\tab `burnPair()`: return YES + NO and recover collateral\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 -\tab `burn()`: burn winning tokens during redemption\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 -\tab Ownership transferred to `MarketFactory` after deployment\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs24\b MarketFactory.sol - Market Factory\b0\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs22 This is the central hub for creating and managing prediction markets.\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 -\tab `createMarket()`: deploys a new AMM pool with seed liquidity\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 -\tab `resolveMarket()`: declares the winning outcome (YES = 1, NO = 2)\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 -\tab `pauseMarket()`: suspends or resumes trading\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 -\tab `distributeFees()`: distributes accumulated fees under the 70 / 20 / 10 split\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 -\tab Access control: owner (Safe multisig) and resolver (can be a separate multisig)\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 -\tab Configurable addresses: treasury, liquidity reserve, emergency reserve, fee collector\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs24\b PronosAMM.sol - Automated Market Maker (CPMM)\b0\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs22 An AMM using the constant product formula ( x * y = k ) with dynamic fees.\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 -\tab Base formula: `x * y = k`, where `x` and `y` are YES / NO reserves\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 -\tab Buy: user deposits USDC, the pool mints YES + NO pairs, and the CPMM computes output tokens\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 -\tab Sell: user returns tokens, a quadratic formula computes collateral out, and the pool burns pairs\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 -\tab Redeem: after resolution, winning tokens are redeemed 1:1 for USDC\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 -\tab On-chain estimate functions: `estimateBuy()`, `estimateSell()`, `priceYes()`, `priceNo()`\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 -\tab All market logic lives on-chain, with no off-chain matching engine\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs24\b Testing\b0\par
