\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs30\b 11. What We Need From a Dev Shop\b0\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs26\b Executive Summary\b0\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs22 About 75% of the product is already built. The smart contracts exist and are tested. The frontend is functional with active Polymarket mode. The backend, including indexer, APIs, and database, is operational.\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs22 What is still needed to reach mainnet:\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs24\b Critical Priority (before June 14)\b0\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 1.\tab Deploy contracts to Arbitrum Sepolia, test them, then deploy to Arbitrum One\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 2.\tab Connect the frontend to the internal contracts (`PronosAMM` buy / sell / redeem)\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 3.\tab Wire the admin panel to contracts via Safe multisig\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 4.\tab Integrate MoonPay for deposits (Apple Pay, Google Pay, cards)\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 5.\tab Integrate UMA Optimistic Oracle for political markets\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 6.\tab Resolve critical and high security issues (C2, C3, H1, H3, H4)\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 7.\tab Run end-to-end testing of the full flow on testnet\par
\pard\li720\tx720\sa80\f0\fs22 8.\tab Load 5 to 10 curated launch markets (World Cup, Liga MX, politics)\par
\pard\sa140\sl300\slmult1\f0\fs24\b Medium Priority (can be post-launch)\b0\par
